{"TopicId":160103,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"explosion based 3D maneuvering system","CreatedByName":"basbr","CreatedById":21492,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T21:23:30Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"basbr","CreatedById":21492,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T21:23:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\na while ago i was stumbling through youtube\u0027s backcatelog\u00A0when i found a old CGI demo, in this video a attack helicopter deploys 2 little drones that seem to navigate by some sort of explosion based maneuvering system.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nis this based on anything in reality? dos this concept have a name and is there any research done into it. is it viable (even in a lower gravity environment) \u00A0i\u0027m very interested it this way of navigating 3D space.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/doteMqP6eSc?start=188\u0026amp;feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SargeRho","CreatedById":25468,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T21:27:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s based on the Multiple Kill Vehicle:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/KBMU6l6GsdM?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022459\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"basbr","CreatedById":21492,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-02T21:33:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223042828\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160103\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493760426\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002225468\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SargeRho\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 minutes ago, SargeRho said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s based on the Multiple Kill Vehicle:\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nah thanks for \u00A0the lead and the quick reply, this is unlike anything i have ever seen before.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Nibb31","CreatedById":7272,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-03T05:17:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose aren\u0027t explosions. They are just \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E jets firing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sevenperforce","CreatedById":157695,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-03T14:11:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223043174\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160103\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493788656\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00227272\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Nibb31\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, Nibb31 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThose aren\u0027t explosions. They are just \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E jets firing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey sort of look like pulsejets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"magnemoe","CreatedById":57801,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-05-03T14:36:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223043458\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022160103\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221493820705\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022157695\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022sevenperforce\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n14 minutes ago, sevenperforce said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThey sort of look like pulsejets.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYes, the \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003Ercs\u003C/abbr\u003E probably has fixed trust so you tune it by using short pulses.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nExtreme accuracy is needed for an anti ballistic missile.\u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd I guess the large engine is just to compensate for gravity, On the real warhead it would probably not be used unless you wanted \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Delta-V\u0022\u003EdV\u003C/abbr\u003E on the warhead for large adjustments like launching mulitple at once. \u00A0\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nAnd it makes no sense for an rocket in atmosphere, Here you would put the engine in back and taken the rocket fast, yes it would not look so cool.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}